.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.backup
*.tfvars
!*.tfvars.example
# Secrets — encrypted OR plaintext — never land in this (public) repo.
# Prod secrets live in the private ../../infra-secrets/disag/ repo. These
# globs guard against an accidental copy being staged here.
secrets.yaml
secrets.json
*.enc.yaml
crash.log
crash.*.log
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json
